This paper discusses the security and integrity of audit logs, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also leverages the design properties of blockchains, which falls under the categories of distributed computing (cs.DC) and databases (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the operational procedures of the proposed system, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper discusses the performance evaluation of the proposed system, which falls under the category of cybernetics (cs.CY).
